                            <comment id="105629" author="yong.fan" created="Wed, 4 Feb 2015 00:45:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I would say that we will only support the rolling upgrade between small versions, such as the patch version difference is within 3. But if rolling upgrade happens between major versions, such as from Lustre-2.6 to Lustre-2.7, it will get failure.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Andreas, what&apos;s your thought for that?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
