                            <comment id="102836" author="yong.fan" created="Thu, 8 Jan 2015 02:59:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;If the OST found that the MDT is running different version, should we forbid the connection? or forbid some LFSCK operations? Or just print some warning message on console?&lt;/p&gt;

